ED_Title: Observer status for the Ramsar Convention on Wetlands Secretariat in the General Assembly
ED_DecisionText: At its 62nd plenary meeting, on 20 December 2018, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the Sixth Committee,  decided to defer a decision on the request for observer status for the Ramsar Convention on Wetlands Secretariat in the Assembly  until the seventy-fourth session of the Assembly.
